        "rich_text_kpamrA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lab Grown Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Lab Grown Diamonds</h3><p>1.]Lower resale value<br/>2.]Still evolving resale infrastructure<br/>3.]Higher value in affordability, sustainability, and aesthetics<br/><br/>For many shoppers, lab grown diamonds provide more overall value because the upfront cost is dramatically lower while the beauty remains identical.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why People Still Choose Lab Grown Diamonds Despite Lower Resale Value",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why People Still Choose Lab Grown Diamonds Despite Lower Resale Value</h2><p>The rising popularity of lab grown diamonds is not driven by resale—it’s driven by smarter value.</p><p>Consumers choose lab grown diamonds because they offer:</p><ul><li>Larger diamonds for the same budget<br/></li><li>Ethical, eco-conscious sourcing<br/></li><li>Premium quality and brilliance<br/></li><li>Modern, stylish designs<br/></li><li>Budget flexibility for future upgrades<br/></li></ul><p>For buyers who prioritize beauty, ethics, and affordability over long-term resale value, lab grown diamonds remain an excellent choice.</p>",
            "custom_id": "why-people",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7bxGmb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Should You Buy Lab Grown Diamonds If Resale Value Matters?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Should You Buy Lab Grown Diamonds If Resale Value Matters?</h3><p>If resale value is your top priority, natural diamonds may be your best choice.</p>",
            "custom_id": "should",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_TTcLbW": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Should_You_Buy_Lab_Grown_Diamonds_If_Resale_Value_Matters.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_yB9GWF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>However, if your priority is:</p><ul><li>Bigger diamonds for your investment<br/></li><li>Ethical sourcing<br/></li><li>Sustainable luxury<br/></li><li>Modern styling<br/></li><li>Excellent visual beauty<br/></li></ul><p>then lab grown diamonds are an exceptional option.</p><p>Most buyers choose lab grown diamonds because they focus on value in the present—not potential resale years later.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>Lab grown diamonds do have resale value, though typically lower than natural diamonds. Their resale pricing is influenced by technology, supply, and evolving market infrastructure. Yet for many buyers, the beauty, ethics, affordability, and exceptional brilliance of lab grown diamonds far outweigh the resale factor.</p><p>If you’re considering adding a lab grown diamond to your collection—whether it’s a timeless engagement ring, a sparkling pair of diamond earrings, or a modern bracelet—choose a jeweler that values craftsmanship, sustainability, transparency, and long-lasting quality.</p><p>Explore ethically crafted, beautifully designed lab grown diamond jewelry that lasts a lifetime.<br/>Discover Lucira’s signature collections and find a piece that truly reflects your style.</p><p>Explore the collection at <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
